args: The decorations are looking great.\nWell done, you two.
Oh, absolutely. This Dragonyule tree\nis stunning.
We didn't celebrate Ilian festivals in\nour homeland, so this is all quite new.
...It would have been nice, though,\nto have a day set aside to spend\nwith loved ones.
Hm? Of course you count as loved ones.\nDon't you worry.
Yes... If nothing else, I should be thankful\nfor the chance to celebrate the occasion\nwith you both.
Thank you for helping with the decorations,\nyou three.
Putting up such a large tree can't have\nbeen easy.
Oh, it was no trouble. These two actually\nquite enjoyed the process.
But if I might ask: why are you dressed\nlike that?
His Highness asked me to deliver presents\nas Saint Starfall.
I shall be visiting the towns and villages\nnearby, so I thought it wise to try the\noutfit on before I left.
Ah, yes. The patron saint of Dragonyule.
His sleigh is driven by reindeer, right?
What's that? You two want to dress up\nfor Dragonyule as well?
I'm sorry, but I don't think they make\noutfits in your size.
Oh, I'm sure I can whip up something.\nConsider it a Dragonyule present.
Would you like one as well?\nYou would make quite the dashing trio.
Er, well... I suppose it couldn't hurt.
That would be wonderful.\nThank you, Cleo.
It was really great of you to make outfits\nfor all three of them. I can't wait to\nsee how they look!
They should be finished changing soon...\nAh, here they are.
Heh. Two little Saint Starfalls, huh?\nI love it.
Sure, but what about the reindeer?\nI was promised reindeer.
Many thanks for this exceptional outfit,\nCleo!
Hold on, YER the reindeer?\nThought for sure it'd be the little guys.
Nonsense. Saint Starfall is the star of\nDragonyule, so it's only right for Fydon\nand Felyx to fill the role.
Besides, Saint Starfall needs a strong\nreindeer to pull his sleigh, right?
Surely there's no one better suited to\nthe task!
I dunno man, I'm pretty sure this is just\nanother ＂Dragon Daddy＂ thing.
It was meant to be a reindeer noise,\nbut I guess I need more practice.
Make sure to thank Cleo for your outfits,\nyou two.
Heh. You are more than welcome.
So, do you three want to help deliver\npresents too?
Would that be all right? They seem quite\nexcited at the prospect.
I would be happy to share some of the\npresents I was set to deliver—
Cease this nonsense at once!\nDragons should NOT play at\nbeing Saint Starfall!
Bestowing presents to people is the job\nof people alone!
What's wrong with a dragon being\nSaint Starfall?
...I tried to give you a chance, Amane,\nbut I won't let you affront dragon\nkind in my presence.
Just... Stop this madness, all right?!
I had thought her distaste for dragons long\nbehind her...
Yeah, it seems like a while since she flew\noff the handle like that.
I must remember she lost her family and\nhome to dragons. She has her reasons\nfor acting the way she does.
Do you still wish to deliver presents?
If so, you will need to leave shortly.
Some people may be scared of Fydon and\nFelyx, or refuse gifts from them.
But I'll be there to speak on their behalf.
After all, if I baby them forever,\nthey'll never grow.
Very well. Then I wish you safe travels.
Perhaps I was a bit too harsh...\nHm? What's that?
Cleo! Why didn't you stop them?!
Calm yourself, Amane.\nThey won't hurt anyone.
I know that—it's not the safety of the\nvillagers I'm worried about!
